  "description": "Oscar at his softest. Whisper-effort with high breath content creates an intimate, ASMR-like vocal texture. Low drama means partials drift independently — a gentle haze rather than a defined voice. Dark filter, slow everything. The sound of someone humming while falling asleep. Safe, warm, present.",
